Document: PhysicsTestMotionResult3D
Path: godot/classes/class_physicstestmotionresult3d.rst
Summary: Stores the result of a physics test motion query in 3D.

PhysicsTestMotionResult3D is a data structure that stores the result of a physics test motion query. It is used by methods like CharacterBody3D.test_motion and PhysicsDirectSpaceState3D.cast_motion to report collision information when moving an object through the physics space.

Inherits: Object < Object
