Document: PhysicsTestMotionResult3D
Path: godot/classes/class_physicstestmotionresult3d.rst
Summary: Describes the motion and collision result from PhysicsServer3D.body_test_motion().

Inherits: Object

This object is created by PhysicsServer3D.body_test_motion() and contains information about the motion test. It is not created by the user.
